graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Operator"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[kserve-webhook-server<br/>Admission Webhooks]
        Controller -.->|manages| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        InferenceGraphCR[InferenceGraph CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModelCR[TrainedModel CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Components"
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Python Init Container]
        Agent[agent<br/>Go Sidecar]
        Router[router<br/>Go Service]
        ModelServer[model-servers<br/>sklearn/xgboost/tensorflow/pytorch/triton]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        KnativeService[Knative Service<br/>Serverless Mode]
        K8sDeployment[Deployment<br/>RawDeployment Mode]
        IstioVS[Istio VirtualService<br/>Traffic Routing]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Knative[Knative Serving 0.26+]
        Istio[Istio 1.15+]
        CertManager[cert-manager 1.9+<br/>or OpenShift service-ca]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API 1.23+]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        ServiceMesh[ServiceMesh/Istio]
        Authorino[Authorino<br/>Authorization]
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Optional]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    User -->|creates| InferenceGraphCR

    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceGraphCR -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModelCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller

    InferenceServiceCR -->|validated/mutated by| Webhook

    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService
    Controller -->|creates| K8sDeployment
    Controller -->|creates| IstioVS

    Controller -->|depends on| Knative
    Controller -->|depends on| Istio
    Controller -->|depends on| CertManager
    Controller -->|uses| K8sAPI

    KnativeService -->|contains| StorageInit
    K8sDeployment -->|contains| StorageInit
    KnativeService -->|contains| Agent
    K8sDeployment -->|contains| Agent
    KnativeService -->|contains| ModelServer
    K8sDeployment -->|contains| ModelServer

    InferenceGraphCR -->|uses| Router

    Controller -->|integrates| ServiceMesh
    Controller -->|integrates| Authorino
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| S3
    Controller -.->|optional| ModelRegistry

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceGraphCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TrainedModelCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ClusterServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Authorino fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
